{"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/workflow\/rendercontext"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"sections":[],"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"major":0,"minor":3},"abstract":[{"code":"RenderContext","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" is the composition point for the workflow tree."}],"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"class"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"RenderContext"},{"kind":"text","text":"<"},{"kind":"genericParameter","text":"WorkflowType"},{"kind":"text","text":"> "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"where"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"WorkflowType"},{"kind":"text","text":" : "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","preciseIdentifier":"s:8WorkflowAAP","identifier":"doc:\/\/Workflow\/documentation\/Workflow\/Workflow","text":"Workflow"}],"platforms":["iOS"],"languages":["swift"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"kind":"content","content":[{"level":2,"type":"heading","anchor":"overview","text":"Overview"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"During a render pass, a workflow may want to defer to a child"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"workflow to render some portion of its content. For example,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"a workflow that renders to a split-screen view model might"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"delegate to child A for the left side, and child B for the right"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"side view models. Nesting allows for a fractal tree that is constructed"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"out of many small parts."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If a parent wants to delegate to a child workflow, it must first"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"create an instance of that workflow. This can be thought of as the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"model of the child workflow. It does not contain any active state,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"it simply contains the data necessary to create or update a workflow"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"node."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The parent then calls ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"render(workflow:outputMap:)"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"with two values:","type":"text"}]},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The child workflow.","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"A closure that transforms the child’s output events into the parent’s"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"code":"Event","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" type so that the parent can respond to events generated by"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the child."}]}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If the parent had previously rendered a child of the same type, the existing"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"child workflow node is updated."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If the parent had not rendered a child of the same type in the previous"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"render pass, a new child workflow node is generated."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The infrastructure then performs a render pass on the child to obtain its"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Rendering"},{"type":"text","text":" value, which is then returned to the caller."}]}]}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/Workflow\/documentation\/Workflow"]]},"kind":"symbol","identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/Workflow\/documentation\/Workflow\/RenderContext","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"metadata":{"modules":[{"name":"Workflow"}],"title":"RenderContext","roleHeading":"Class","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","t